Canada Outlook - July 2017 
As 2017 moves past the halfway point, many countries continue to loosen their fiscal straitjackets to support economic growth. This year will likely be remembered as the transition to more synchronized global growth. 
The Bank of Canada clearly signaled that Canada is part of this global trend in its latest Monetary Policy Report on July 12. 


